data.title: Fall of 2023 Dean’s List
data.meta_description: Dean's List students have a minimum 3.5 grade point average, successfully completing at least 12 semester hours, excluding Pass/No Pass work.
data.text:
Paula Powers

Share:

Achieving a position on the Dean’s List at Clemson University is a noteworthy accomplishment. This esteemed recognition is conferred upon students who attain a minimum 3.5 grade point average while successfully completing at least 12 semester hours, excluding Pass/No Pass coursework.

Below is a comprehensive listing of the Fall 2023 Dean’s List, sorted alphabetically, according to last names.

To commemorate this momentous achievement, visit the University’s President’s and Dean’s List website. On the site, you have the opportunity to generate a personalized badge by inputting a student’s name. You will be able download an image to save, send or share as a celebration of their academic success.
